title: Naruto Shippuden Season 16 (349-361) Complete EngSub
description:
Hey there my fellow Naruto Fans...Its been an year since I last uploaded Naruto episodes. Sry for that been busy with stuff. And I noticed there is still no compiled episodes of Season 16/17/18 etc at all so here is Season 16 from episode 349 to 361 complete. If there is any type of error or missing episode let me know in the comments section and i'll correct it. I have downloaded these episodes from different sources and gathered them all up in one folder for your viewing pleasure.

I'll be uploading the rest of the series very soon....

A thanks will be very appreciated and Please seed when you have finished downloading so others can download as well
